dct_title_s: Proposed Dredging in Cooper River for North Side Improvements East of Kaighn Ave. to Grove St. Application by Camden County Park Commission
dct_description_sm: Map shows Cooper River from Kaighn Ave. to Grove Street.
Shows Collingswood Borough, Haddon Township, Pennsauken Township, and Delaware Township. Map also shows are to be dredged in the future, filled with dredged materials, and dredged along Cooper River.
